{"tid":2165243,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[DGX]聽完『這地』之後有的想自殺…","createTime":"2020-08-19T16:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T16:38:50.000Z","uid":248120,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"167f10838c9e4838b41678a59cdda546c9af6b26","tid":2165243,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">醜話在先：撐榮光，請買野<br />\n切勿唱黃歌後不顧而去！</span><br />\n<br />\n之前聽左下DGX新出既『這地』<br />\n有種滄桑但又幾典雅既感覺<br />\n睇到個MV又好似明白佢背後事理<br />\n<br />\n但呢輪唔明點解<br />\n我越聽越灰<br />\n感覺入面既「轉折」係唔會到來<br />\n正如黑夜過後你保證唔到黎明會到來<br />\n尤其是出左單色動畫版之後<br />\n個答案係更加悲觀左<br />\n<br />\n明明一隻寄託希望既歌<br />\n我越聽越覺得自己離死亡越來越近<br />\n感覺一切願景、希望唔會係我呢一世人當中發生<br />\n而實現願望既方法就係自行死去<br />\n還生到另一個世界<br />\n<br />\n唔係因爲我太痛苦<br />\n唔係因爲有人威脅我<br />\n而係因爲我想係另外一個世界繼續我既人生<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">（又或者「光香時革五訴缺不」並唔係我理想）</span><br />\n<br />\n查實我就唔相信所謂「七生報國論」、「前世來世」呢的論說<br />\n但呢隻歌無可否認係有紀念逝者既成分<br />\n<strong><br />\n我無意貶抑或批判呢首歌或創作者<br />\n我亦無刻意曲解呢首歌或者佢既世界觀</strong><br />\n但我估唔到自己聽完呢隻黃歌<br />\n竟然可以萌生到死意<br />\n我係咪對唔住同路人？<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;或者其實我咁樣係侮辱緊佢？"},{"pid":"7e2870e0c33699fef829a61480a4ccf3ebb71a3f","tid":2165243,"uid":238660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"手足，頂住呀，香港要人"},{"pid":"73a8c9d9fa394b5396384e2cd8a5178596ff0d4a","tid":2165243,"uid":140893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好 唯有講句加油<br />\n建議聽下I vow to the my country"},{"pid":"82164ecc2455e223d84668ce16249b68678358ed","tid":2165243,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0befacbba2a1a50102562f69fed2a530d0d137f6","tid":2165243,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你睇彩色版啦，正能量好多！"},{"pid":"ad54985a820cd8e9fae3165049ae487d5d4bcb18","tid":2165243,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"1b0039a38e0b359431d70cae3edd64495e13deef","tid":2165243,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3sAoTzPP0wQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3sAoTzPP0wQ&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=761738d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3sAoTzPP0wQ</a>"},{"pid":"317d54486da4ef437d4ec733c2f9ab0e98a11bb2","tid":2165243,"uid":61002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:26:21.000Z","msg":"每一次都想喊，係願榮光之後唯一一首有咁嘅感覺"},{"pid":"7d840f87577583b331d9fb75fc0126f453ac0426","tid":2165243,"uid":105976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"每人都有獨特理解係正常<br />\n<br />\n我地下首歌就黎出啦<br />\n有溫柔風 有正面風  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e717b645d446206448a070d54e42156811bb478f","tid":2165243,"uid":267622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"不如聽下阿李近幾首歌<br />\n個人灰時聽返啲灰啲嘅嘢可能好啲"},{"pid":"338954c92b5ecb31dde116e50b10638005252f0b","tid":2165243,"uid":214554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"想阻你幾分鐘聽一首歌...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2170921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2170921</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}